{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128930/extras/new-banner-1.gif?t=1730906381\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Dust &amp; Courage: Jake Bolton\u2019s Journey is an<strong> isometric single-player RPG</strong> set in a historical fantasy rendition of Wild West America. This adventure is as much yours as it is Jake Bolton's! Shape the game with your dialogue choices, determining who becomes your enemy and your friend. Customize your character and become the cowboy you want to be in this sandbox experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128930/extras/banner-1.png?t=1730906381\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Preview the world of <i>Dust &amp; Courage: Jake Bolton\u2019s Journey</i> and experience a sneak peek of the full game\u2019s thrilling Wild West adventure. In this demo, you\u2019ll explore a unique map, separate from the main game, designed to introduce you to the core gameplay mechanics and immerse you in Jake Bolton\u2019s story.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128930/extras/header-no-3-3.gif?t=1730906381\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128930/extras/banner-2.png?t=1730906381\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Gear up with a range of melee weapons and firearms, testing your skills in combat or diplomacy. Along the way, you\u2019ll encounter a variety of characters, unlock new outfits through quests or purchase them from shops, and make impactful decisions that echo throughout your journey.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This demo offers a taste of the full experience, showcasing the strategic combat, dialogue-driven choices, and rich storytelling that define <i>Dust &amp; Courage</i>. Your adventure starts here\u2014whether you resolve conflicts with words or bullets is up to you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128930/extras/header-no-5.gif?t=1730906381\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128930/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1730906381","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128930/page.bg.jpg?t=1730906381","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128930/75d1638b75a48c86156eb2eec2ae1023d3efd70a/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1730906381","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128930/75d1638b75a48c86156eb2eec2ae1023d3efd70a/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1730906381","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Game demo","id":10},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Captions available","id":13},{"description":"Steam Cloud","id":23}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128930/extras/new-banner-1.gif?t=1730906381\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Dust &amp; Courage: Jake Bolton\u2019s Journey is an<strong> isometric single-player RPG</strong> set in a historical fantasy rendition of Wild West America. This adventure is as much yours as it is Jake Bolton's! Shape the game with your dialogue choices, determining who becomes your enemy and your friend. Customize your character and become the cowboy you want to be in this sandbox experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/